# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# __xor__ dict-presence — operator.contains(Cls.__dict__, '__xor__')
#
# All 8 multiprocessing classes return false for __xor__.
# managers._BaseSetProxy proxies set, and set defines __xor__ for symmetric
#   difference (s ^ t). However, _BaseSetProxy does NOT define __xor__ in
#   its own __dict__. Symmetric-difference through the proxy is accessed
#   via the _method IPC callthrough mechanism, not via a locally defined dunder.
# managers.BaseListProxy: proxies list — list has no __xor__.
# managers._BaseDictProxy: proxies dict — dict has no __xor__.
# Process/Pool/AsyncResult/MapResult/SyncManager: process-management and
#   result-handle types; XOR is not defined for any of them.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

